title: ArcGIS Portal Log Settings
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: MIT
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors ArcGIS Portal log level and log retention settings.

 WARNING, WARN, and SEVERE log levels are considered OK by default. INFO is WARN
 by default. OFF is WARN by default. DEBUG, FINE, FINER, FINEST, and VERBOSE are
 CRIT by default.

 Retention is checked against a configurable expected range.
item:
 This check has no item.
discovery:
 One service is discovered when Portal log settings are present.
